keyword_info: Boat charters in Key West refer to the service of renting out boats for personal use in the Key West area of Florida. These charters can be used for various activities such as fishing, sightseeing, snorkeling, or simply enjoying the beautiful waters around the Florida Keys. Boat charters can range from small personal boats to larger yachts, and they often come with experienced crew members to guide and assist you. This service offers a unique, personalized way to explore and enjoy the natural beauty and marine life of Key West.

reddit_summaries.boat charters key west:
1. Choosing Excursions: Many Reddit users are seeking advice on choosing between various boat charters and tours in Key West. A popular topic of discussion is deciding between a half-day seaplane trip to Dry Tortugas and a charter boat trip to the sandbars. Opinions are generally split, with some recommending the uniqueness and views of the seaplane trip, while others suggest the relaxing and enjoyable experience of the boat trip.

2. Job Opportunities: There are discussions around job opportunities in Key West, particularly in the boating and fishing charter industry. Some users share their experiences and insights on the financial viability of such jobs, with a focus on living conditions for those earning under $40k a year.
